## Components Reference

All imports from `cds-react-components/src/components`.

### Button
```tsx
import { Button } from "cds-react-components/src/components";
<Button variant="primary|secondary|outline" size="large|small|xsmall" inverse={false} label="Continue" icon={<Icon />} />
```

### Input
```tsx
<Input label="Email" helperText="We'll never share this" icon={<Icon />} placeholder="you@example.com" />
```

### Badge
```tsx
<Badge color="gray|green|blue|white|neutral" label="Active" statusDot={false} />
```

### Header
```tsx
<Header header="Title" description="Subtitle text" position="page|section|interstitial" />
```

### Tabs
```tsx
<Tabs tabs={[{ id: "t1", label: "Tab 1" }]} activeTab="t1" onTabChange={(id) => {}} />
```

### TabBar
Bottom navigation bar with built-in icon set.
```tsx
import { TabBar, CK_TABS, TT_TABS } from "cds-react-components/src/components";
<TabBar variant="tt|ck" tabs={TT_TABS} activeTab="home" onTabChange={(id) => {}} showLabels={false} showAiButton={true} />
```
Pre-configured presets: `CK_TABS`, `CK_TABS_MARKETPLACE`, `TT_TABS`.

### Toolbar
Top app bar with status bar, AI search, navigation.
```tsx
<Toolbar type="ck-l0|tt-l0|ck-l1|tt-l1|tt-assisted|tt-assisted-l1|tt-vignettes|l2|l2-dark" progress={true} progressValue={50} showStatusBar={true} />
```
The `tt-assisted` variant shows an expert avatar + Intuit AI logo combo in the search pill with a green status dot. Pass `expertImageSrc` to provide the expert photo.
```tsx
<Toolbar type="tt-assisted" expertImageSrc="/expert.jpg" />
```
TT vignettes (CCP glass toolbar — tax return pill + inline progress):
```tsx
<Toolbar type="tt-vignettes" progressValue={18} vignetteLabel="Chloe's 2026 taxes" onVignetteClick={() => {}} />
```

### MetricTile
```tsx
<MetricTile variant="blue|tan" type="money|credit" label="Checking" value="$6,356" changeText="5% this month" />
```

