## Icons Reference

All imports from `cds-react-components/src/icons`. Every icon accepts `{ className?: string }` and uses `currentColor`.

| Category | Icons |
|----------|-------|
| Navigation | `HomeIcon`, `ChevronLeftIcon`, `MenuIcon`, `MoreIcon` |
| Commerce | `CartIcon`, `CardIcon`, `CashIcon`, `MoneyBagIcon`, `MarketplaceIcon` |
| Content | `FolderIcon`, `LightbulbIcon`, `ShieldCheckIcon` |
| Alerts | `NotificationIcon`, `CheckmarkIcon` |
| iOS Status | `CellularIcon`, `WifiIcon`, `BatteryIcon` |
| Misc | `BenefitCircleIcon` |

```tsx
import { HomeIcon, CartIcon } from "cds-react-components/src/icons";
<HomeIcon className="size-6 text-blue-6" />
```

