## When building new components

If the UI you need does not exist above, you may create a new component. It MUST:

1. Use TypeScript with an exported `Props` interface
2. Use Tailwind classes with CDS design tokens (no raw hex for colors that have tokens)
3. Accept a `className?: string` prop
4. Follow the same file pattern as existing CDS components
5. Be a candidate for future inclusion in the CDS library
